'''Mačevo''' ({{lang-mk|Мачево}}) is a village in the [[Berovo Municipality]] of [[Republic of Macedonia|Macedonia]].

==Notable people==
*[[Metodi Stamboliski]], Macedonian general and Chief of General Staff of the Army of the Republic of Macedonia.

